'''Organisashon Mundial di Salú''' (WHO) ta un agensia spesialisa di [[Nashonan Uni]] ku responsabilidat pa salubridat públiko internashonal.<ref>[https://www.kff.org/global-health-policy/fact-sheet/the-u-s-government-and-the-world-health-organization/  The U.S. Government and the World Health Organization], The Henry J. Kaiser Family Foundation</ref> Su konstitushon, den kual struktura i prinsipionan di WHO ta stipulá, ta splika ku su meta prinsipal ta pa asegurá "alkanse pa tur hende di e nivel mas haltu di salubridat posibel".<ref>[http://apps.who.int/gb/bd/pdf_files/BD_49th-en.pdf#page=7 WHO Constitution, BASIC DOCUMENTS, Forty-ninth edition], World Health Organization</ref> 

[[File:World Health Organisation building south face 2.jpg|thumb|left|Sede prinsipal di WHO na Ginabra]]
Organisashon Mundial di Salú a establese dia [[7 di aprel]] [[1948]], riba kual fecha ta konmemorá anualmente ''Dia Mundial di Salú''.<ref>[https://www.who.int/about/who-we-are/history History], World Health Organization</ref> Sede prinsipal di WHO ta na [[Ginebra]], [[Suisa]], ademas di su seis ofisina regional semi-outonomo i 150 ofisina local ront mundu. Na 2017 [[Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus]] a keda  elegí komo sekretario general di WHO. 


